data.description: Stunning 3-4 BR w Loft, Pond View, Storage & Tasteful Decor.  Fantastic florplan designed for comfort and style. Nestled in a sweet neighborhood, this home boasts an array of features that will surely captivate your heart. You'll be greeted by an inviting open entryway & family room that sets the tone for the entire home. Seamless flow of the layout enhances the spacious feel, allowing for easy movement throughout the main level. This exquisite home offers 3 BRs, bonus & storage areas providing ample space for relaxation & privacy. The upstrs loft/bnus rm offers a versatile space that can be customized to fit your lifestyle, whether it's a cozy entertainment area, a home office, or playrm. Full fenced back yd. Shows like a model home!
